item.description: Come join us and make a gypsum altar piece, wall hanging or statue.Gypsum has many magical properties and Its sure to be a fun, possibly a little messy, but definitely a rewarding time crafting your own artwork. Cost is $15 pp to choose from a huge array of mythical, fantasy, celestial, pagan and nature inspired designs. Would request for attendies to bring a little something for a pot luck snack intermission while projects dry.
item.name: Gypsum Plaster Casting Class
